tool.help:
What it does ============
Calculates the number of "core" OTUs shared by groups given thresholds for how frequent the OTUs should be above a certain abundance. Also returns the average abundance of the OTUs in a particular group.
The Galaxy tool calls the `amp_venn <https://kasperskytte.github.io/ampvis2/reference/amp_venn.html>`_ function of the ampvis2 package.
@HELP_RELATIVE_ABUNDANCES@
Input =====
@HELP_RDS_INPUT@
@HELP_METADATA_LIST_INPUT@
Output ======
A venn diagram in the chosen output format.
